        <p>You can pin your favorite fonts <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare">and font sets </MadCap:conditionalText>so they will appear at the top of the list. This makes them easier to find later. Pinned fonts<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare"> and font sets</MadCap:conditionalText> appear in a group that you can expand or collapse. This is a way to limit the list of fonts to those that you use the most and hide from view those that you do not use. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.AnalyzerOnlineOnly,Products.ContributorOnlineOnly,Products.FlareOnlineOnly">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../Fonts/Using_Font_Groups.htm">Using Font Groups.</MadCap:xref></MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Capture">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../Fonts/Using_Font_Groups_Capture.htm">Using Font Groups</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Mimic">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../Fonts/Using_Font_Groups_Mimic.htm">Using Font Groups</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
